{
  "readme": {
    "type": "root",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "A "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://qiime2.org",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "QIIME 2"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " plugin "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://develop.qiime2.org",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "developed"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " by Colin Wood (colin.wood@nau.edu). 🔌"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "depth": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Important: This package should be considered alpha software"
          }
        ],
        "identifier": "important-this-package-should-be-considered-alpha-software",
        "label": "Important: This package should be considered alpha software",
        "html_id": "important-this-package-should-be-considered-alpha-software",
        "implicit": true
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Because the underlying qSIP2 package is relatively new and only cursory user testing & validation of this software has been performed, the package should be considered experimental."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "depth": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Installation instructions"
          }
        ],
        "identifier": "installation-instructions",
        "label": "Installation instructions",
        "html_id": "installation-instructions",
        "implicit": true
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "depth": 3,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Install Prerequisites"
          }
        ],
        "identifier": "install-prerequisites",
        "label": "Install Prerequisites",
        "html_id": "install-prerequisites",
        "implicit": true
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://conda.io/miniconda.html",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "Miniconda"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " provides the "
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "conda"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " environment and package manager, and is currently the only supported way to install QIIME 2.\nFollow the instructions for downloading and installing Miniconda."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "After installing Miniconda and opening a new terminal, make sure you’re running the latest version of "
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "conda"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": ":"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "bash",
        "value": "conda update conda"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "depth": 3,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Install development version of "
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "q2-qsip2"
          }
        ],
        "identifier": "install-development-version-of-q2-qsip2",
        "label": "Install development version of q2-qsip2",
        "html_id": "install-development-version-of-q2-qsip2",
        "implicit": true
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Next, you need to get into the top-level "
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "q2-qsip2"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " directory.\nYou can achieve this by "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/creating-and-managing-repositories/cloning-a-repository",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "cloning the repository"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": ", for example with the command:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "shell",
        "value": "git clone https://github.com/caporaso-lab/q2-qsip2"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Once you have the directory on your computer, change ("
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "cd"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": ") into it."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "If you’re in a conda environment, deactivate it by running "
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "conda deactivate"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Then, run:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "shell",
        "value": "conda env create -n q2-qsip2-dev --file ./environments/q2-qsip2-qiime2-amplicon-2026.1.yml"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "After this completes, activate the new environment you created by running:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "shell",
        "value": "conda activate q2-qsip2-dev"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Finally, run:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "shell",
        "value": "make install"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "depth": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Testing and using the most recent development version of "
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "q2-qsip2"
          }
        ],
        "identifier": "testing-and-using-the-most-recent-development-version-of-q2-qsip2",
        "label": "Testing and using the most recent development version of q2-qsip2",
        "html_id": "testing-and-using-the-most-recent-development-version-of-q2-qsip2",
        "implicit": true
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "After completing the install steps above, confirm that everything is working as expected by running:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "shell",
        "value": "make test"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "You should get a report that tests were run, and you should see that all tests passed and none failed.\nIt’s usually ok if some warnings are reported."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "If all of the tests pass, you’re ready to use the plugin.\nStart by making QIIME 2’s command line interface aware of "
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "q2-qsip2"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " by running:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "shell",
        "value": "qiime dev refresh-cache"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "You should then see the plugin in the list of available plugins if you run:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "shell",
        "value": "qiime info"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "You should be able to review the help text by running:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "lang": "shell",
        "value": "qiime qsip2 --help"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "depth": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Accessing the usage tutorial"
          }
        ],
        "identifier": "accessing-the-usage-tutorial",
        "label": "Accessing the usage tutorial",
        "html_id": "accessing-the-usage-tutorial",
        "implicit": true
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "You can find instructions for performing an example analysis with q2-qsip2 in the "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://github.com/colinvwood/q2-qsip2/blob/main/tutorial/tutorial.md",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "tutorial"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": ".\nThe data files that you’ll need to run that tutorial can be downloaded from "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://github.com/colinvwood/q2-qsip2/tree/main/tutorial",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "the directory containing the tutorial"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "Have fun! 😎"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "depth": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "About"
          }
        ],
        "identifier": "about",
        "label": "About",
        "html_id": "about",
        "implicit": true
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "The "
          },
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "q2-qsip2"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " Python package was "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://develop.qiime2.org/en/stable/plugins/tutorials/create-from-template.html",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "created from template"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": ".\nTo learn how to use QIIME 2, refer to the "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://docs.qiime2.org",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "QIIME 2 User Documentation"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": ".\nTo learn QIIME 2 plugin development, refer to "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://develop.qiime2.org",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "emphasis",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "Developing with QIIME 2"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "inlineCode",
            "value": "q2-qsip2"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " is a QIIME 2 community plugin.\nMore information on development and support for community plugins can be found "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://library.qiime2.org",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "here"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": ".\nIf you need help with a community plugin, first refer to the "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "www.qiime2.org",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "project website"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": ".\nIf that page doesn’t provide information on how to get help, or you need additional help, head to the "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://forum.qiime2.org/c/community-contributions/community-plugins/14",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "Community Plugins category"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " on the QIIME 2 Forum where the QIIME 2 developers will do their best to help you."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
